"""
STEP 5: 验证与误差结构（混淆矩阵与 PCA 分离图）

Scope
-----
Only Step 5 is executed. This script reuses Step 4's frozen train/test split,
refits only the Step 4-selected best model, exports train/test confusion matrices,
exports Satin-focused error summaries, fits PCA on training rows only, projects the
test rows into the same PCA space, and writes plot-ready F05 data.

No SHAP, endpoint classification, threshold sensitivity, or later-step conclusion
is computed here. PNG is intentionally deferred because the current execution rule
is "先生成分析数据，最后一步才允许绘图".

Key audit constraint
--------------------
Step 3 may contain target-derived audit columns such as class_*, step3_*,
route_a_* and expected_main_test_*. These columns are valid audit metadata, but
must never enter model reconstruction or PCA. This script uses only the nine
locked oxide fields and reuses results/04_train_test_split.csv; it never creates
a new random split.
"""

