# 7. Output table builders
# Reference: user-provided locked plan, Step 4 output files.
# Modification Reason: 可审计性; outputs are separated into sample-level split records,
# fold-level CV metrics, model-level comparison, locked config YAML, and plot-ready F04 CSV.
